TopicTitle: Hey, anyone remember that fan made Mun Map?

Articles.Content:
I remember there was this Mun map with areas marked with names... but for the life of me I cannot find the thing. Search engine is being its usual self as it is blind to words with 3 letters or less and of course... MUN is three letters. So to this forum the Mun does not exist.

So, anyone remember where it was?
I remember the one where you had to build a rocket to get back from the moon but not this one...
